<br>
First spell I failed to research was Greater summoning: Air, which is lvl 49...<br>
<br>
Remember also that nearly all research is about pets, and some are available at merchants in the Ocean of Tears (16 and 20 pets) and in Katta castellum (some 39 and all 44). Those merchants have also a couple researched non-pet spells.<br>
